  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The changes of local pulmonary ventilation should be registered with an electric impedance
      tomography (EIT) before and after a dilatative tracheotomy. The hypothesis is that the EIT
      cannot show changes in local ventilation due to the tracheotomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
